subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Epiphanny Prince scored 26 points and had a career-high seven steals, helping No. 5 Rutgers beat visiting Saint Joseph’s, 86-59, in the opener for both teams Friday.
